uote>三叔做咩依家唔出pure android edition,</blockquote><br />\n依加啲人居然吹奉無做野好過有做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實當android仲要吹奉pure android嘅時候證明android仲都好唔成熟，用家寧願少啲功能都想部機運作正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好諷刺"},{"pid":"852ffb0dc78efa24d9528920f67f7bb5ee0ed7d4","tid":348930,"uid":30830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:38:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三叔做咩依家唔出pure android edition,</blockquote><br />\n依加啲人居然吹奉無做野好過有做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實當android仲要吹奉pure android嘅時候證明android仲都好唔成熟，用家寧願少啲功能都想部機運作正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好諷刺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我咁諗<br />\n廠商加好多嘢都未必啱心水<br />\n咁我梗係要最簡潔嘅系統自己慢慢執，慢慢搵啱用嘅嘢"},{"pid":"18b702e8db44aa3f7a668804612bfd5266d02ded","tid":348930,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:46:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三叔做咩依家唔出pure android edition,</blockquote><br />\n依加啲人居然吹奉無做野好過有做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實當android仲要吹奉pure android嘅時候證明android仲都好唔成熟，用家寧願少啲功能都想部機運作正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好諷刺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我咁諗<br />\n廠商加好多嘢都未必啱心水<br />\n咁我梗係要最簡潔嘅系統自己慢慢執，慢慢搵啱用嘅嘢</blockquote><br />\n廠家加鹽加醋係為左扮個os係佢出嘅姐，商業性裝飾當然唔夠pure android 好，以當中最垃圾嘅三叔touchwiz 黎講，就更加係影衰android 之作，垃圾中嘅冠軍。<br />\n所以玩android, 一定要揀pure android 或盡量接近pure android 為好。"},{"pid":"c492b6cbe79878c48b8a30333afd90a5b1550113","tid":348930,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:47:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講又比人話<br />\n唔講又比人話</blockquote><br />\n有咩想講你咪講囉，又唔會ban你嘅，依家比你講呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24fec53f0132af7b66b3e39ce908ea40930b612b","tid":348930,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T01:02:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三叔做咩依家唔出pure android edition,</blockquote><br />\n依加啲人居然吹奉無做野好過有做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實當android仲要吹奉pure android嘅時候證明android仲都好唔成熟，用家寧願少啲功能都想部機運作正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好諷刺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我咁諗<br />\n廠商加好多嘢都未必啱心水<br />\n咁我梗係要最簡潔嘅系統自己慢慢執，慢慢搵啱用嘅嘢</blockquote><br />\n我覺得唔用可以唔理就算，講到cpu幾勁幾多ram，但係裝左個app放係到唔用都怕整慢部機有啲諷刺（大陸app銀眼就另計）<br />\n<br />\n而且pure效能係唔係最勁都唔肯定，就算有10000同10050嘅分別。<br />\n<br />\nAnyway，裝得多app部機會慢始終係一個誤區（定係android真係咁？）"},{"pid":"35de45ca3226c788e8a995936345541eca5e7967","tid":348930,"uid":5846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T01:04:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三叔做咩依家唔出pure android edition,</blockquote><br />\n依加啲人居然吹奉無做野好過有做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實當android仲要吹奉pure android嘅時候證明android仲都好唔成熟，用家寧願少啲功能都想部機運作正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好諷刺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我咁諗<br />\n廠商加好多嘢都未必啱心水<br />\n咁我梗係要最簡潔嘅系統自己慢慢執，慢慢搵啱用嘅嘢</blockquote><br />\n廠家加鹽加醋係為左扮個os係佢出嘅姐，商業性裝飾當然唔夠pure android 好，以當中最垃圾嘅三叔touchwiz 黎講，就更加係影衰android 之作，垃圾中嘅冠軍。<br />\n所以玩android, 一定要揀pure android 或盡量接近pure android 為好。</blockquote><br />\n但明明用家係buy佢部機buy佢個brand先買，廠商有自己風格其實有道理"},{"pid":"0475ab710001607088428a988798e5c52287c09b","tid":348930,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T01:14:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三叔做咩依家唔出pure android edition,</blockquote><br />\n依加啲人居然吹奉無做野好過有做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實當android仲要吹奉pure android嘅時候證明android仲都好唔成熟，用家寧願少啲功能都想部機運作正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好諷刺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我咁諗<br />\n廠商加好多嘢都未必啱心水<br />\n咁我梗係要最簡潔嘅系統自己慢慢執，慢慢搵啱用嘅嘢</blockquote><br />\n廠家加鹽加醋係為左扮個os係佢出嘅姐，商業性裝飾當然唔夠pure android 好，以當中最垃圾嘅三叔touchwiz 黎講，就更加係影衰android 之作，垃圾中嘅冠軍。<br />\n所以玩android, 一定要揀pure android 或盡量接近pure android 為好。</blockquote><br />\n但明明用家係buy佢部機buy佢個brand先買，廠商有自己風格其實有道理</blockquote><br />\n寫得好就話buy姐，屎米加監控三叔垃圾touchwiz 點buy法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以玩android 就要首選pure android 呀"},{"pid":"f05f66244bc742beceb34e4df7c673b001dc7d4e","tid":348930,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T02:27:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三叔做咩依家唔出pure android edition,</blockquote><br />\n依加啲人居然吹奉無做野好過有做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實當android仲要吹奉pure android嘅時候證明android仲都好唔成熟，用家寧願少啲功能都想部機運作正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好諷刺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我咁諗<br />\n廠商加好多嘢都未必啱心水<br />\n咁我梗係要最簡潔嘅系統自己慢慢執，慢慢搵啱用嘅嘢</blockquote><br />\n廠家加鹽加醋係為左扮個os係佢出嘅姐，商業性裝飾當然唔夠pure android 好，以當中最垃圾嘅三叔touchwiz 黎講，就更加係影衰android 之作，垃圾中嘅冠軍。<br />\n所以玩android, 一定要揀pure android 或盡量接近pure android 為好。</blockquote><br />\n但明明用家係buy佢部機buy佢個brand先買，廠商有自己風格其實有道理</blockquote><br />\n寫得好就話buy姐，屎米加監控三叔垃圾touchwiz 點buy法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以玩android 就要首選pure android 呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買得三星話唔定就係貪佢廢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50464f3858ed9cfb2